@var{gcontext}, @var{id-choice}, @var{pixmap}, and @var{window}
errors, the keyword-value pairs are the core error pairs plus:

@multitable @columnfractions 0.5 0.5
@item @var{:resource-id} @tab @var{card32}
@end multitable

