pairs plus:

@multitable @columnfractions 0.5 0.5
@item @var{:atom-id} @tab @var{card32}
@end multitable

For @var{:value} errors, the keyword-value pairs are the core error
pairs plus:

@multitable @columnfractions 0.5 0.5
@item @var{:value} @tab @var{card32}
@end multitable

